2Ô∏è‚É£  Lost & Found

> Intelligent lost and found portal using natural language processing to suggest potential item matches.



‚úÖ Key Features:

Students can post lost or found items with description, image, location

match suggestion (based on similarity of descriptions)

Claim/Resolve feature when item is returned

Status-based filter (Active, Claimed)



---

3Ô∏è‚É£ Study Group Hub

> A collaborative space for students to connect via subject-specific discussion groups.



‚úÖ Key Features:

